## Description

FTPS? what's that, we just use good old FTP here, no need for all that encryption overhead. 

## Solution

>wireshark, open ./dump.pcapng.
>see around, find FTP-DATA protocol
>also find user: `sebi` and pass: `dadada`
>copy the data hexdump
>paste into [Cyberchef](https://gchq.github.io/CyberChef/#recipe=From_Hex('Auto')&&oeol=FF)
>save the result to file: `Secrets.kbdx`
>try local keepass, fail
>go to https://app.keeweb.info/, open file, upload file, use password: `dadada`
>there's flag in an entry, as a password
